{"tid":210280,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"求教，咩叫氹人，咩野叫關心？","createTime":"2017-04-20T20:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T01:27:43.000Z","uid":105104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f595054e2e03076d236fef32c5a0f284107597f","tid":210280,"uid":105104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T20:21:31.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916abe6a72ea90d14ba3c6b3489320276ad0d186","tid":210280,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T20:46:26.000Z","msg":"有目的 冇目的"},{"pid":"f9e7235985e091ab7dd652c66c6d0855c1fc7fdf","tid":210280,"uid":105104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T21:13:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有目的 冇目的</blockquote><br />\n咁做咩先可以氹人or feel到係關心？"},{"pid":"0b330bd7b795909cc31b10bd1a784e4f89df6edf","tid":210280,"uid":63055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T21:20:46.000Z","msg":"如果佢鍾意你<br />\n 你挖舊鼻屎卒落佢塊面黎氹佢都會開心"},{"pid":"53433d942e8fa37d73dffe172cc79a7f57cf29d4","tid":210280,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T22:26:09.000Z","msg":"氹人 係有目的地想令一個人開心 而個目的可能只係「想佢開心」咁簡單 咁你可能就會搞下爛gag 送下小禮物 甚至講一句甜言蜜語<br />\n<br />\n而 關心 係無目的地想一個人好 例如你會關心人地食左飯未 凍有無著多件衫 呢啲野對你無直接利益 而多數人做呢啲行為都係發自內心<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up"},{"pid":"5b38fb7e7b8e89b21034bd5f406d00a3bff617a0","tid":210280,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:02:53.000Z","msg":"一個字「錢」<br />\n<br />\n請食飯 送禮物<br />\n有車管接送<br />\n間唔中去吓旅行"},{"pid":"48eee3b940d3624f0116eadcf274557d70f2fc6c","tid":210280,"uid":105104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢鍾意你<br />\n 你挖舊鼻屎卒落佢塊面黎氹佢都會開心</blockquote><br />\n佢應該會打柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47856e7d1feeb2775e990ca64087dc0237112a98","tid":210280,"uid":105104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>氹人 係有目的地想令一個人開心 而個目的可能只係「想佢開心」咁簡單 咁你可能就會搞下爛gag 送下小禮物 甚至講一句甜言蜜語<br />\n<br />\n而 關心 係無目的地想一個人好 例如你會關心人地食左飯未 凍有無著多件衫 呢啲野對你無直接利益 而多數人做呢啲行為都係發自內心<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up</blockquote><br />\n想佢開心，但係佢開唔開心就得佢自己知。好似做咩都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6106478b687d7a1336ff5da9149b0bd2e6db0c1f","tid":210280,"uid":105104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個字「錢」<br />\n<br />\n請食飯 送禮物<br />\n有車管接送<br />\n間唔中去吓旅行</blockquote><br />\n咁如果冇錢呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884d3ce5dd35fe6a68f36dff77cde4dd76bcee2e","tid":210280,"uid":82126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"比佢感覺到你係著緊佢既已經好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不過當然要睇下你係佢邊個[/size=2[size=2]]</span><span style=\"color: pink;\"></span>"},{"pid":"5d509acc6879dfe55cfbe5963d8a065d32e7cba8","tid":210280,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"唔識氹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e34691ee91bcbe6a52389cf33a37f29ee996296","tid":210280,"uid":73281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意你既做咩都只係騷擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc3b578658e40aa9d544d387f5771749cd92810","tid":210280,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"兜野較剪腳車落佢個頭<br />\n一隻手插落佢對眼度<br />\n一隻手插落個屎忽度<br />\n之後挖佢對眼同條腸出黎煲湯餵狗"},{"pid":"78b77ab68a8115f7a853431dd59f4e32e3c64822","tid":210280,"uid":105104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識氹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class